== Access ==
The shrine is approximately 1.5 km north of {{ill|Hitachi-Ōta Station|ja|常陸太田駅|12=draft|12=draft}} on the {{ill|East Japan Railway Company|ja|東日本旅客鉄道|12=draft|12=draft}} (JR). It is a 20-minute walk.

