== Access ==
The shrine is approximately 1.5 km north of {{ill|Hitachi-Ōta Station|ja|常陸太田駅|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hitachi-Ōta Station|qq=}} on the {{ill|East Japan Railway Company|ja|東日本旅客鉄道|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/East Japan Railway Company|qq=}} (JR). It is a 20-minute walk.

